<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Registration - {{ event.title }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #1e7e34;
        }
        .event-details {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .verification-note {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>‚úÖ Verify Your Registration</h1>
        <p>{{ event.title }}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{ attendee.name }}!</h2>
        
        <p>Thank you for registering for <strong>{{ event.title }}</strong>! To complete your registration and gain access to event materials, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{ verify_url }}" class="button">üîê Verify Email & Complete Registration</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="event-details">
            <h3>Event Details:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Title:</strong> {{ event.title }}</li>
                <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{ event.startDate|date('F j, Y \\\\a\\\\t g:i A') }}</li>
                {% if event.endDate %}
                    <li><strong>End Date:</strong> {{ event.endDate|date('F j, Y \\\\a\\\\t g:i A') }}</li>
                {% endif %}
                {% if event.location %}
                    <li><strong>Location:</strong> {{ event.location }}</li>
                {% endif %}
            </ul>
            
            {% if event.description %}
                <p><strong>About this event:</strong></p>
                <p>{{ event.description|nl2br }}</p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        
        <div class="verification-note">
            <h4>üìã What happens after verification?</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>‚úÖ Your registration will be confirmed</li>
                <li>üìÅ You'll get access to event materials and downloads</li>
                <li>üîë You can use the "Already Registered?" login on the event page</li>
                <li>üìß You'll receive updates about the event</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>Important:</strong> This verification link is unique to your email address and will expire after 24 hours. If you didn't register for this event, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        
        <p>If the button above doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <p style="word-break: break-all; font-family: monospace; background-color: #e9ecef; padding: 10px;">{{ verify_url }}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent automatically by the Event Management System.<br>
        Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        
        <p>Having trouble? Contact the event organizer for assistance.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>